'''Antilles BioGen''' (ABG), according to the [[Medical droid/Legends|medical droid]] [[2-1B/Legends|2-1B]], was the manufacturer of the [[L-hand 980]], which was used as a [[Cybernetics/Legends|prosthesis]] for [[Luke Skywalker/Legends|Luke Skywalker]] after he lost his [[Duel on Cloud City/Legends|duel]] with [[Anakin Skywalker/Legends|Darth Vader]]. While the arm which goes with the hand was discontinued, the 980 continued being produced.<ref name="Dear 2-1B" />

{{Company-stub}}

